The article is a fact sheet on immigration issued on January 16, 2018. It highlights the priorities of President Donald J. Trump, which include defending the country, protecting communities, and prioritizing the safety of the American people. The fact sheet mentions a report released by the Department of Justice (DOJ) and the Department of Homeland Security (DHS) that focuses on the entry of foreign-born terrorists into the United States through the immigration system. It also mentions the report shedding light on acts of gender-based violence committed against women by foreign nationals. Lastly, the fact sheet calls for an end to chain migration and the visa lottery, stating that the current immigration system jeopardizes national security.